room_title: Escape room "Battle Behind Bars" by Riddle Me Roanoke in Roanoke
room_description: You have been jailed for a crime you didn't commit, but the evidence against you is strong, so you are not likely to get out any time soon.  Rumor has it that a recent inmate in your cell had an escape plan all ready to use, but he ended up getting released on a technicality. No one has figured out the escape plan yet, so give it your best shot before the guards discover it!
